  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The advertisement, by reason of its inappropriate design, scale and location, comprises an unsympathetic and incongruous feature, that will result in the unsightly proliferation and clutter of signage in this location, that would be harmful to the character and appearance of the site and wider setting of the South Shoreditch Conservation Area. As such, the proposal would be contrary to policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and HC1 (Heritage conservation and growth) of the London Plan (2021) and policies LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets) and LP7 (Advertisements) of Hackney&#x27;s Local Development Plan (2020) and the Shopfront Design Guide and the South Shoreditch Conservation Area Appraisal (2017).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
